channel.title: Whats going on?!?
channel.description:
Hiya ;)
I downloaded maoparscape client around a week ago, it was working fine til' the other day when i could only log in once and then when it logged me out ii couldnt log back in! :( Then yesterday i was not able to log in at all!! even if i can log in it will log me out within 20 minutes. I HAVE the latest version of java I HAVE re-installed it but it wont work!!
I also downloaded other clients like silabs v4 but it will not load completely and other clients will hardly let me log in?? :confused: :( it cant be my internet cause' that works fine and im puzzled!!
please help me out. Cheers, Kratos00
